high_descs: Turn around and move to the stove, then turn left to face the counter to the left of the stove.
Pick up the sharp knife with the yellow handle from the counter.
Turn left and carry the knife to the white table in front of the window on your right.
Use the knife to slice the apple on the back right corner of the table.
Turn around and carry the knife to the other white table, which has shelves below, on the opposite wall.
Place the knife in the bowl closest to you on the table.
Turn back around and move to the table with the apple.
Pick up a slice of apple from the table.
Turn right, carry the apple slice to the stove, and then head right again to the microwave.
Place the apple slice in the microwave and then remove once heated.
Turn right and carry the apple slice to the white table with shelves below on your left.
Place the apple slice on the table.
anns.task_desc: Move a heated slice of apple to the white table with shelving below.

high_descs: Go to the counter near the stove
Pick up the knife from the counter
Go to the small white table
Cut the apple
Turn around to the big white table
Place the knife down in a bowl on the table
Turn around to the small white table
Pick up an apple piece
Go to the microwave
Heat the apple piece
Go to the big white table
Place the apple down on the big white table
anns.task_desc: Place a heated apple slice on the large table

high_descs: Turn around go to sink and stove.  Turn left, go to counter with knife and mug.
Pick up knife from counter, left of the mug.
Turn left, proceed to table on right.  Turn right to face table with pump dispensers.
Slice potato on back of table, behind salt shaker.
Turn around, go to table across room.
Put knife in bowl closest to you on table.
Turn around, go to table with sliced potato on it.
Pick up slice of potato off of table.
Turn right go to stove.  Turn around, go across room to microwave.
Put potato in microwave, wait three seconds, remove potato from microwave.
Turn right, to to table on left.  Turn left to face table.
Place potato on table, in front of fork, to the right of the knife with the yellow handle.
anns.task_desc: Pick up knife, slice potato, put knife in bowl, heat slice of potato in microwave, put potato on table.
